quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  39,64,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Muri kundikomekedza kunamata zvimwe (zvisikwa) here kunze kwaAllah, imi vasina kukwana"
  39,65,"Uye zvirokwazvo zvinodzikiswa kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) sekunge kune avo vakanga variko usati wavapo: “Kana ukava unosanganisa Allah nezvimwe mukunamata, zvirokwazvo mabasa ako achange asina maturo, uye zvirokwazvo uchange uri pakati peavo vakarasikirwa.”"
  39,66,"Nokudaro! Namata Allah (Voga), uye wova pakati peavo vanotenda"
  39,67,"Uye havana kupa Allah kodzero yavo yakakwana. Uye pazuva rekutongwa pasi rose richabatwa muruoko rwavo uye matenga akaputirwa ari muruoko rwavo rwerudyi. Kurumbidzwa ngakuve kwavari, uye vari pamusoro pezvavanovasanganisa nazvo"
  39,68,"Uye hwamanda icharidzwa, uye zvose zviri mumatenga uye zvose zviri pasi zvichakomoka (zvichafa) kusara kweanodiwa naAllah. Uye icharidzwa kechipiri, uye zvirokwazvo vachava vanomira vakatarisa"
  39,69,"Uye pasi pachapenya nechiedza chaTenzi waro (apo vachauya kunotonga vanhu), uye bhuku richava rinoiswa, uye maporofita nevapupuri vachava vanounzwa pamberi; uye vachava vanotongwa pakati pavo nechokwadi, uye havazodzvinyirirwa"
  39,70,"Uye umwe neumwe achave anopihwa mubairo wakazara wezvaaiita, uye (Allah) vanoziva zvikuru zvavanoita"